oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Birthday party at the Jones home
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of several women and children gathered on a front porch for a birthday party at the J. Jones home formerly located at 426 East Chester Street in Jackson, Tennessee. Many of the children are seated in highchairs. "Dr. J.T. Jones" is engraved on the top step.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Women; Children; Porches
